# -*- mode: conf; -*-

IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
User svend@svends.net
PassCmd "@pass@/bin/pass show general/imap.fastmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
Path ~/.mail/fastmail/ # must append a slash to specify an entire directory
Inbox ~/.mail/fastmail/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
Near :fastmail-local:
Patterns *
# Sync Both
Create Near
Expunge Near
SyncState *
